something exciting is going to happen

04:23.963 --> 04:26.465
in the pork belly market this morning.

04:40.146 --> 04:43.274
Will Miss Penelope
be dining with you this evening, sir?

04:43.941 --> 04:46.277
Yes. Yes, she will.

05:28.444 --> 05:30.946
