- Morning, Folsey.

05:40.831 --> 05:42.917
- Morning, Mr Winthorpe.
- Good morning.

05:43.376 --> 05:45.419
- Morning, Mr Winthorpe.
- Morning.

05:46.962 --> 05:49.215
